Title: Honeycomb
Writer: Rafael Azcona (story), Rafael Azcona, Geraldine Chaplin (story), Geraldine Chaplin, Carlos Saura (idea), Carlos Saura (story), Carlos Saura
Actors: Geraldine Chaplin, Per Oscarsson, Teresa del Río, Julia Peña
Plot: Teresa is like a child. She is frustrated with her childless existence and suspects her husband of being unfaithful. She and her husband play games with each other, tempting fate.
